Extract Transformation: Get a Date Component
In the Transform node of a Data Prep recipe, select the date column you want to extract a component from.
Select which date component to extract.
Under Show Results In, select whether the new values appear in a new column and whether to keep the original column.
If you elect to create a column, set the label under Column Label.
Click Apply to add the transformation to the Transform node.
The Preview tab shows the new date component column.
To view the Graph area, click the Collapse button ().
Save the recipe.

After you run the recipe, the selected date component is extracted in the specified text (dimension) column.
title: Extracting Date Components in CRM Analytics
